snippet.textDisplay: I am a Korean. Re: Wendy's accident on the stage - There  are safety issue in Korea.  Be careful when you travel to Korea. Their mind set is NOT that good on safety. 1)  After the accidents, they don't research comprehensively such as doing the root cause analysis (RCA) and secondary cause analysis, etc  and don't  take  necessary measures as a new regulation, a rule or formal additional step. They just think "That was a mistake and careful next time" . This means they think the accident was done by a person, not a system or missed step.  So, the same accidents do happen again by other guys.  2)  The safety in NOT the first priority on their mind set.  The efficiency and the speed are always on the top.
